------------change resolution -------------------

ffmpeg -i output_home2.mp4 -s 512x384 output_home2.avi

------------change fps ----------------

ffmpeg -i input.mov -sameq -r 24 -y output.mov


change fps with time -----
ffmpeg -i test.avi -f rawvideo -b 50000000 -pix_fmt yuv420p -vcodec rawvideo -s 512x384 -y temp.raw
ffmpeg -f rawvideo -b 50000000 -pix_fmt yuv420p -r 29.61 -s 512x384 -i temp.raw -y output.avi


-----------combine matteucci---------------------

ffmpeg -i landing.avi -vf "[in] scale=iw/1:ih/1, pad=2*iw:ih [left]; movie=landing_stabilized.avi, scale=iw/1:ih/1, fade=out:300:30:alpha=1 [right]; [left][right] overlay=main_w/2:0 [out]" -b:v 768k Output.avi

